---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Animations from '../components/Animations.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Orangesoft — Digital Agency Since 2007"
  description="Orangesoft is a Malaysian digital agency with 19+ years of experience building websites, applications, and digital solutions for corporate clients across Southeast Asia."
>
  <header class="co-header">
    <div class="co-header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="logo">Orangesoft<span class="dot">.</span></a>
      <nav class="co-nav">
        <a href="/about" class="co-nav-link co-nav-link--active">About</a>
        <a href="/careers" class="co-nav-link">Careers</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="co-nav-link">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="inner">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Building the Digital<br />Future Since 2007</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        Orangesoft is a Malaysian digital agency specialising in web design, development, and digital marketing. For over 19 years, we have helped organisations across Southeast Asia build digital experiences that drive measurable business outcomes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="stats" data-animate="stagger">
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat-val" data-target="600" data-decimals="0" data-suffix="+">0+</span><span class="stat-label">Projects Delivered</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat-val" data-target="19" data-decimals="0" data-suffix="+">0+</span><span class="stat-label">Years in Business</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat-val" data-target="5" data-decimals="0" data-suffix="">0</span><span class="stat-label">Service Divisions</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat-val" data-target="4.9" data-decimals="1" data-suffix="/5">0/5</span><span class="stat-label">Client Satisfaction</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="inner">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Divisions</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Five specialised divisions, each focused on delivering excellence in their domain.</p>
      <div class="divisions" data-animate="stagger">
        <a href="/custom" class="division">
          <span class="div-num">01</span>
          <h3>Custom Websites & Applications</h3>
          <p>Bespoke digital solutions built with NuxtJS, Laravel, and Strapi for organisations that demand more than templates.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/wordpress" class="division">
          <span class="div-num">02</span>
          <h3>WordPress Websites</h3>
          <p>Professional WordPress solutions that balance creative ambition with robust, scalable architecture.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/kentico" class="division">
          <span class="div-num">03</span>
          <h3>Kentico Websites</h3>
          <p>Sophisticated enterprise CMS solutions built for scale, security, and seamless content workflows.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/support" class="division">
          <span class="div-num">04</span>
          <h3>Support & Maintenance</h3>
          <p>Proactive care and continuous optimisation so your digital presence never misses a beat.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/seo" class="division">
          <span class="div-num">05</span>
          <h3>SEO</h3>
          <p>Strategic search optimisation that positions your brand where it matters most.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="inner" data-animate="fade-up">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="story">
        <p>Founded in 2007 in Kuala Lumpur, Orangesoft began as a small web design studio with a simple belief: every business deserves a digital presence that truly represents them.</p>
        <p>Over nearly two decades, we have grown from a two-person operation into a multi-disciplinary agency serving corporate clients across Malaysia, Singapore, and the wider Southeast Asian region. Along the way, we have delivered over 600 projects spanning corporate websites, custom web applications, e-commerce platforms, and digital marketing campaigns.</p>
        <p>Today, our five specialised divisions allow us to offer focused expertise while maintaining the personal service that has defined us from the beginning. Whether you need a high-performance custom application or a well-maintained WordPress site, there is an Orangesoft team dedicated to exactly that.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="inner" data-animate="fade-up">
      <h2 class="section-title">Where We Are</h2>
      <div class="location">
        <p class="location-city">Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia</p>
        <p class="location-note">Serving clients across Malaysia, Singapore, and Southeast Asia. We work with teams globally via video calls and shared project dashboards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="inner" data-animate="fade-up">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Ready to Work Together?</h2>
        <p>Whether you have a clear brief or just an idea, we would love to hear from you.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="co-footer">
    <div class="co-footer-inner">
      <a href="/" class="footer-logo">Orangesoft<span class="dot">.</span></a>
      <nav class="footer-nav">
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/careers">Careers</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 Orangesoft. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <Animations />
</Layout>

<style>
  .co-header { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  .co-header-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
  .logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-foreground); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .dot { color: var(--color-brand); }
  .co-nav { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .co-nav-link { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; }
  .co-nav-link:hover, .co-nav-link--active { color: var(--color-foreground); }
  .co-nav-link--active { font-weight: 600; }

  .section { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
  .inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-alt { background: white; }
  .section-dark { background: var(--color-surface-dark, #1C1917); }

  .hero { padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
  .hero-title { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--color-foreground); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .hero-lead { font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-muted); max-width: 640px; }

  .section-title { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-foreground); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .section-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

  .stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .stat-val { display: block; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-foreground); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .stat-label { display: block; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: 0.25rem; }

  .divisions { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .division { display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 1.75rem; border: 1px solid var(--color-divider); border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease; }
  .division:hover { border-color: var(--color-brand); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .div-num { font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-brand); letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .division h3 { font-size: 1.0625rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-foreground); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .division p { font-size: 0.8125rem; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-muted); }

  .story { max-width: 720px; }
  .story p { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .story p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .location { text-align: center; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .location-city { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-brand); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .location-note { font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-muted); }

  .cta-block { text-align: center; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .cta-block h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .cta-block p { font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .btn { display: inline-flex; padding: 0.875rem 2rem; background: var(--color-brand); color: white; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 0.375rem; transition: background-color 0.3s ease; }
  .btn:hover { background: var(--color-brand-dark, #C45E0A); }

  .co-footer { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-divider); }
  .co-footer-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
  .footer-logo { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-foreground); text-decoration: none; }
  .footer-nav { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .footer-nav a { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; }
  .footer-nav a:hover { color: var(--color-foreground); }
  .footer-copy { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    .stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .divisions { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .co-footer-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .footer-nav { flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
